From 2d266f24653dffecfc95c7384cfa7760766a72ae Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Lucas <lucas@eliteaero.com.br>
Date: Tue, 28 Apr 2026 12:38:36 +0200
Subject: [PATCH 3/3] Fix assert pattern and add TP>1 guard comment in
 _create_padded_weight_param

Replace `assert ..., ValueError(...)` (which raises AssertionError with a
ValueError *object* as its message) with a proper `if ... raise ValueError(...)`.

Add comment on the `> 1` guard explaining that single-slot layers need no
merge and that shard_offset_map is absent for them (relevant for TP>1 where
only one slot may land on a given rank).

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>

Signed-off-by: Lucas <lucas@eliteaero.com.br>
